name: podamShouldFillPojoInterfaceAttributeIfFullConstructorSetsItsValue

testSteps.description: Given a Podam Factory with external factory uk.co.jemos.podam.test.unit.features.externalFactory.TestExternalFactory@1a5a2a2

Then the two objects uk.co.jemos.podam.test.unit.features.externalFactory.TestExternalFactory@1a5a2a2 and uk.co.jemos.podam.test.unit.features.externalFactory.TestExternalFactory@1a5a2a2 should be equal
When I invoke the factory to manufacture class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.PojoWithInterfaces with the fullest constructor
Then the object uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.PojoWithInterfaces@883888 should not be null
Then the two objects 2 and 2 should be equal
Then the two objects interface uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.ObjectExt and interface uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.ObjectExt should be equal
Then the two objects interface uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.InterfacePojo and interface uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.InterfacePojo should be equal
Then the two objects 2 and 2 should be equal

title: Podam should fill POJOs and interface attributes if a full constructor sets the interface attribute value
